lead_paragraph: Manchester United's 2-1 Premier League win over relegation-threatened Swansea City on Saturday has eased the pressure on their "angry" players, manager Louis van Gaal has said.

headline.print_headline: 'Angry' United Players Breathing Easy After Swansea Win-Van Gaal
